<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Ph.D. Student in Computer Science and Engineering, CUHK</p>
      <h1>Mingjun Wang</h1>
      <p class="tagline">AI for EDA, circuit representation learning, fault simulation, and 3D IC design.</p>
      <p class="bio-lead">
        I am a Ph.D. student in the Department of Computer Science and Engineering at The Chinese University of Hong Kong, advised by Prof. Bei Yu. My research focuses on AI-assisted chip design and verification, spanning multi-modal circuit understanding, RTL-to-layout prediction, 3D IC design automation, and efficient fault simulation for reliable digital systems.
      </p>
      <p class="bio-lead">
        Before CUHK, I received my master's degree in Electronic Information from the University of Chinese Academy of Sciences and the Institute of Computing Technology, Chinese Academy of Sciences, advised by Prof. Xiaowei Li at the State Key Laboratory of Processors. I received my bachelor's degree in Microelectronics Science and Technology from Peking University.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions" aria-label="Profile links">
        <a class="button primary" href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=E9aUbvAAAAAJ&amp;hl=en">Google Scholar</a>
        <a class="button" href="assets/files/Mingjun_Wang_CV.pdf">CV</a>
        <a class="button" href="https://github.com/xin-xi-xiao">GitHub</a>
        <a class="button" href="#publications">Selected Work</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-metrics" aria-label="Profile metrics">
        <div><strong>CUHK CSE</strong><span>Ph.D. student</span></div>
        <div><strong>ICML Spotlight</strong><span>RTLDistil 2025</span></div>
        <div><strong>Best Paper Nominations</strong><span>ICCAD 2024 / ASP-DAC 2025</span></div>
      </div>
      <p class="motto"><span>Guiding motto</span> Unity of Knowledge and Action: knowledge is the beginning of action; action is the completion of knowledge. Wang Yangming</p>
    </div>
    <aside class="portrait-panel" aria-label="Portrait and affiliations">
      <div class="portrait-wrap">
        <img src="assets/img/mingjun-wang.jpg" alt="Portrait of Mingjun Wang" />
      </div>
