      <div><time>2026</time><p><strong>DAC 2026:</strong> ATLAS was accepted to DAC for FIT prediction with asynchronous topological learning.</p></div>
      <div><time>2025</time><p><strong>ICML 2025 Spotlight:</strong> RTLDistil was selected as a Spotlight paper for RTL-level timing prediction.</p></div>
      <div><time>2025</time><p><strong>DAC 2025:</strong> MOSS and EPICS appeared at DAC, covering sequential-circuit representation learning and parallel fault simulation.</p></div>
      <div><time>2024</time><p><strong>ICCAD 2024:</strong> DDP-Fsim was selected as a Best Paper Award Candidate.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

