  <section id="experience" class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="section-kicker">Experience and Projects</p>
      <h2>Research threads that shaped my current agenda</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="project-grid">
      <article class="project-card">
        <span>Jul. 2023 - Present</span>
        <h3>Fault Simulation Research</h3>
        <p>Developed hardware-aware and parallel fault simulation frameworks at the State Key Laboratory of Processors, ICT, CAS, targeting practical speedups over commercial flows.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="project-card">
        <span>May 2024 - Present</span>
        <h3>Circuit Multi-Modal Dataset and ML Applications</h3>
        <p>Built multi-modal circuit datasets and learning pipelines for functionality prediction, timing and power estimation, and circuit representation extraction.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="project-card">
        <span>Sep. 2021 - Present</span>
        <h3>Industrial EDA Experience at CASTEST</h3>
        <p>Contributed to functional-safety analysis tools and digital-circuit fault simulation platforms, including ISO 26262-oriented workflows for automotive-grade chips.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="project-card">
        <span>Sep. 2020 - Jun. 2022</span>
        <h3>RRAM-Based True Random Number Generator</h3>
        <p>Designed and implemented a true random number generator based on RRAM for my undergraduate thesis, with randomness validated by the NIST statistical test suite.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

